						<p>This is U-KNOW PLUS. We build an automatic urine collection system to make it even more user-friendly. By pressing the button, your urine is automatically collected and sent to our column. Through U-KNOW PLUS, the U-Know detection causes us no inconvenience to our daily life.</p>
						<p>Therefore, you can use it every day to know about your glucose level without invasive monitoring detection.</p>

