						<p>Step THREE: Receive the result on the screen. The signal can be send to an app connecting with U-KNOW, so the users are able to track the result through via smart devices, such as smart phone and Apple Watch.</p>

						<div class="title-line">Structure of U-KNOW</div>
						<video class="demo-video" controls>
